cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.SE, cs.SC. 

The paper deals with the termination of higher-order term rewriting, which is a topic in both logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The introduction of a new rewrite formalism and a modular dependency pair framework suggests a focus on formal methods (cs.FL) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the implementation of the framework in a higher-order termination tool suggests a focus on scientific computing (cs.SC).
